                                            Before starting any business, we need to decide first thing whether we are going to do business alone or along with someone else. If the answer comes we will start business with someone else, we have been lot of options like partnership firm, limited liability partnership firm, joint venture, public limited company & private limited company etc. So, Public limited company is one of the available varieties among lot of options to start business with someone else.
                                        </p>
